    <h1>Login</h1>
    <h2>Basic Path</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><p>The software prompts for the Inventory Manager's usr
	  name.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software prompts for the Inventory Manager's
	  password. As the Inventory Manager enters the password
	  it is shown using astricks. </p></li>
      <li><p>The Inventory Manager enters his or her user name and
	  password.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software lookups the database's host name. </p></li>
      <li><p>The software lookups the database's dbname.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software checks that the database is a mysql database.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software attempts to connect to the database
	  using the entered username and password.</p></li>
    </ol>

